<br />
New York, Museum of Modern Art, 20th Century Portraits, December 9, 1942–January 24, 1943, p. 141; traveled to Baltimore Museum of Art, February 12–March 7, 1943; and Worcester Art Museum, March 24–April 18, 1943.<br />
